<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<section class="page-header page-header--center" style="padding-bottom:56px;">
  <span class="eyebrow" style="display:inline-block;">Pricing</span>
  <h1 class="display" style="font-size:clamp(40px,6.4vw,72px);">Engagements built<br>around outcomes.</h1>
  <p class="lede" style="margin:0 auto;max-width:560px;">Every brand&rsquo;s starting point is different. Pick the scope that fits — we&rsquo;ll tailor the plan on your strategy call.</p>
</section>

<section class="container" style="padding:20px 24px 40px;">
  <div class="grid-seam grid-seam--2col">
    <div class="price-card">
      <div class="price-card__tier">Visibility Audit</div>
      <div class="price-card__amount">One-time</div>
      <p class="price-card__desc">Know exactly where you stand before you invest a dollar in growth.</p>
      <div class="price-card__features">
        <div class="price-card__feature"><span>&#8250;</span><span>Brand, visibility &amp; AI-search gap analysis</span></div>
        <div class="price-card__feature"><span>&#8250;</span><span>Where you&rsquo;re losing time, trust &amp; attention</span></div>
        <div class="price-card__feature"><span>&#8250;</span><span>Prioritized roadmap &amp; quick wins</span></div>
      </div>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--secondary btn--small">Request an audit</a>
    </div>

    <div class="price-card price-card--featured">
      <div class="price-card__head">
        <div class="price-card__tier price-card__tier--accent">Growth Program</div>
        <span class="badge badge--accent">MOST POPULAR</span>
      </div>
      <div class="price-card__amount">Monthly</div>
      <p class="price-card__desc">The full program, run every cycle &mdash; branding, visibility, AI, and automation working as one system.</p>
      <div class="price-card__features">
        <div class="price-card__feature"><span>&#8250;</span><span>Everything in the audit, continuously</span></div>
        <div class="price-card__feature"><span>&#8250;</span><span>Branding, content &amp; website improvements</span></div>
        <div class="price-card__feature"><span>&#8250;</span><span>Search &amp; AI-search visibility</span></div>
        <div class="price-card__feature"><span>&#8250;</span><span>Automation, AI &amp; monthly reporting</span></div>
      </div>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary btn--small">Book a strategy call</a>
    </div>

    <div class="price-card">
      <div class="price-card__tier">Enterprise</div>
      <div class="price-card__amount">Custom</div>
      <p class="price-card__desc">Multi-brand, multi-market visibility with dedicated strategy and priority delivery.</p>
      <div class="price-card__features">
        <div class="price-card__feature"><span>&#8250;</span><span>Dedicated strategist &amp; team</span></div>
        <div class="price-card__feature"><span>&#8250;</span><span>Custom tooling &amp; dashboards</span></div>
        <div class="price-card__feature"><span>&#8250;</span><span>Cross-market prompt coverage</span></div>
      </div>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--secondary btn--small">Talk to us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p style="margin:26px 0 0;text-align:center;font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.06em;color:var(--text-faint);">Pricing tailored to scope &middot; no long lock-ins &middot; cancel with 30 days&rsquo; notice</p>
</section>

<%- include('partials/faq') %>

<section class="cta-band section--top-border" style="margin-top:60px;">
  <div class="cta-band__inner">
    <h2>Let&rsquo;s scope it together.</h2>
    <p>A 30-minute call is all it takes to see where you stand and what it&rsquo;ll take to win the answer.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Book a strategy call</a>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
